'''第51届奥斯卡颁奖典礼'''是[[电影艺术与科学学院|电影艺术与科学学院]]旨在奖励[[1978年电影|1978年电影]]的颁奖晚会，于[[太平洋时区|太平洋时区]]1979年4月9日晚7点（[[北美东部时区|北美东部时区]]晚10点）在洛杉矶[[多萝西·钱德勒大厅|多萝西·钱德勒大厅]]举行，共计颁发22类[[奥斯卡金像奖|奥斯卡金像奖]]（又称学院奖）。晚会通过[[美国广播公司|美国广播公司]]直播，小杰克·海利制作，马蒂·帕赛塔执导<ref>{{cite news | via = Google News Archive | title = War Film, Comedy Head List | access-date = 2021-03-24 | date = 1979-04-06 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1338&dat=19790406&id=Mv1LAAAAIBAJ&pg=4405,1962767 | work = Spokane Daily Chronicle | publisher = Cowles Publishing Company | page = 7}}</ref>，谈话节目主持、喜剧演员[[约翰尼·卡森|约翰尼·卡森]]首度担任主持人<ref>{{cite news | title = Frank Won't Sing Without G Notes | work = Chicago Tribune | date = 1978-10-03 | page = 136}}</ref>。[[格里高利·派克|格里高利·派克]]与[[克里斯托弗·里夫|克里斯托弗·里夫]]三天前在加利福尼亚州[[比佛利山|比佛利山]][[比弗利希尔顿酒店|希尔顿酒店]]颁发[[奧斯卡科技成果獎|奧斯卡科技成果獎]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Past Scientific & Technical Awards Ceremonies | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/scitech/pastawards.html | publisher = [[电影艺术与科学学院|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]] | access-date = 2014-10-07 | dead-url = yes | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141007214118/http://www.oscars.org/awards/scitech/pastawards.html | archive-date = 2014-10-07 }}</ref>。

《[[猎鹿人|猎鹿人]]》获包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]在内的五项大奖<ref>{{cite news | last = Siskel | first = Gene | title = Oscars to Fonda, Voight, 'Hunter' | url = http://archives.chicagotribune.com/1979/04/10/page/1/article/oscars-to-fonda-voight-hunter | work = Chicago Tribune | date = 1979-04-10 | access-date = 2016-03-08 | dead-url = no | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160308182052/http://archives.chicagotribune.com/1979/04/10/page/1/article/oscars-to-fonda-voight-hunter/ | archive-date = 2016-03-08 }}</ref>。其他获奖电影包括拿下三项大奖的《[[荣归_(电影)|荣归]]》、获奖两项的《[[午夜快車|午夜快車]]》，以及胜出一项的《[[巴迪霍利传|巴迪霍利传]]》、《[[加州套房|加州套房]]》、《[[天堂之日|天堂之日]]》、《[[尼罗河上的惨案_(1978年电影)|尼罗河上的惨案]]》、 《[[神鹰之战|神鹰之战]]》、《[[掏出你的手帕|掏出你的手帕]]》、《[[上错天堂投错胎|上错天堂投错胎]]》、《[[恐怖监狱|恐怖监狱]]》、《[[特别快递|特别快递]]》、《[[超人_(電影)|超人]]》、《[[少年父亲|少年父亲]]》和《[[狂热周五夜|狂热周五夜]]》。晚会的电视直播吸引4630万美国观众收看，[[尼爾森收視率|尼爾森收視率]]达34.6<ref name="Viewership" /><ref name="Boca" />。

== 晚会 ==
本届颁奖典礼在[[洛杉磯市中心|洛杉磯市中心]]的[[多萝西·钱德勒大厅|多萝西·钱德勒大厅]]举行，深夜谈话节目主持人[[约翰尼·卡森|约翰尼·卡森]]首度主持奥斯卡晚会<ref>{{cite news | via = Google News Archive | last = Thomas | first = Bob | title = Oscar Show-A Thankless Chore | access-date = 2021-03-24 | date = 1979-04-09 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=110&dat=19790409&id=ItNOAAAAIBAJ&pg=6936,8014761 | work = Ludington Daily News}}</ref>。[[杰克·艾略特|杰克·艾略特]]（{{lang|en|Jack Elliott}}）与[[艾林·弗格森|艾林·弗格森]]（{{lang|en|Allyn Ferguson}}）担任电视直播音乐总监<ref name="Osborne-2013" />{{rp|413}}。歌手[[小萨米·戴维斯|小萨米·戴维斯]]（{{lang|en|Sammy Davis Jr.}}）和[[斯蒂夫·劳伦斯|斯蒂夫·劳伦斯]]（{{lang|en|Steve Lawrence}}）表演曲目《奥斯卡也是人》（{{lang|en|Oscar's Only Human}}），由未获[[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖|原创歌曲奖]]提名的电影歌曲片段组合而成<ref name="Wiley-Bona-1996">{{cite book | last1 = Wiley | first1 = Mason | last2 = Bona | first2 = Damien | title = Inside Oscar: The Unofficial History of the Academy Awards | url = https://archive.org/details/insideoscarunoff0000wile | year = 1996 | isbn = 978-0-3454-0053-6 | location = New York, New York, United States | edition = 5 | oclc = 779680732 | publisher = Ballantine Books}}</ref>{{rp|560}}。电影艺术与科学学院音乐组起初抗议并要求晚会上不要表演这首歌，但在海利以辞职并取消邀请卡森主持要挟后保留<ref>{{cite book | last = Pond | first = Steve | title = The Big Show: High Times and Dirty Dealings Backstage at the Academy Awards | year = 2005 | isbn = 978-0-5712-1193-7 | location = New York, New York, United States | publisher = [[费伯出版社|Faber and Faber]] | url = https://archive.org/details/bigshowhightimes00pond | page = 29 | access-date = 2021-03-24}}</ref>。

奥斯卡影帝[[約翰·韋恩|約翰·韋恩]]上台颁发[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片奖]]时现场嘉宾起立致敬，这也是他最后一次在公开场合露面<ref name="Osborne-2013" />{{rp|251}}。两个月后，韦恩因[[胃癌|胃癌]]在6月11日谢世，享年72岁<ref name="Osborne-2013" />{{rp|251}}<ref>{{cite news | last = Hammond | first = Pete | title = How Michael Cimino's 'The Deer Hunter' Pioneered The Modern Day Oscar Campaign – And Won | url = https://deadline.com/2016/07/michael-ciminos-deer-hunter-oscar-campaign-win-best-picture-1201782549/ | access-date = 2021-03-24 | work = [[Deadline_Hollywood|Deadline Hollywood]] | date = 2016-07-03 | archive-date = 2020-11-08 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201108161929/https://deadline.com/2016/07/michael-ciminos-deer-hunter-oscar-campaign-win-best-picture-1201782549/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[杰克·海利|杰克·海利]]（{{lang|en|Jack Haley}}）是晚会制作人小杰克·海利的父亲，他与合作出演《[[綠野仙蹤_(1939年電影)|绿野仙踪]]》的[[雷·博尔格|雷·博尔格]]（{{lang|en|Ray Bolger}}）一起颁发[[奥斯卡最佳服装设计奖|最佳服装设计奖]]，这也是老海利最后一次公开露面<ref>{{cite news | last = Smith | first = J.Y. | title = Jack Haley Dies, Was Tin Man in 'The Wizard of Oz' | url = https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/local/1979/06/07/jack-haley-dies-was-tin-man-in-the-wizard-of-oz/2c6b95f4-2ec3-49a5-bf62-4b09596f6642/ | work = [[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]] | date = 1979-06-07 | access-date = 2021-03-24 | archive-date = 2019-04-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190401114319/https://www.washingtonpost.com/archive/local/1979/06/07/jack-haley-dies-was-tin-man-in-the-wizard-of-oz/2c6b95f4-2ec3-49a5-bf62-4b09596f6642/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 获奖与提名 ==
1979年2月20日，学院主席[[霍华德·科克|霍华德·科克]]（{{lang|en|Howard W. Koch}}）与女演员[[苏珊·布莱克利|苏珊·布莱克利]]公布第51届奥斯卡金像奖提名<ref>{{cite news | last = Thomas | first = Bob | title = 1978 Oscar nominees announced | work = San Bernardino Sun | date = 1979-02-21 | page = C1}}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = The Deer Hunter, Heaven Can Wait top honors Oscar nominees listed | work = [[环球邮报|The Globe and Mail]] | date = 1979-02-21 | page = P11}}</ref>。《[[猎鹿人|猎鹿人]]》与《上错天堂投错胎》（{{lang|en|''Heaven Can Wait''}}）均以九项提名领跑<ref>{{cite news | last = Grant | first = Lee | title = Two War Films on Oscar Ballot | work = [[洛杉磯時報|Los Angeles Times]] | date = 1979-02-21 | page = D1}}</ref>。获奖名单在4月9日的颁奖典礼揭晓<ref>{{cite news | last = Harmetz | first = Aljean | title = 2 Vietnam Films Cast Aside Ghosts on Way to Oscars | url = https://www.nytimes.com/1979/04/11/archives/2-vietnam-films-cast-aside-ghosts-on-way-to-oscars-new-york.html | access-date = 2021-03-24 | work = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | archive-date = 2020-11-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201112215758/https://www.nytimes.com/1979/04/11/archives/2-vietnam-films-cast-aside-ghosts-on-way-to-oscars-new-york.html | date = 1979-04-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[沃伦·比蒂|沃伦·比蒂]]与[[巴克·亨利|巴克·亨利]]均因《上错天堂投错胎》获[[奥斯卡最佳导演奖|最佳导演奖]]提名，是[[杰罗姆·罗宾斯|杰罗姆·罗宾斯]]与[[罗伯特·怀斯|罗伯特·怀斯]]合作执导《[[西城故事_(1961年電影)|西区故事]]》后首次有两位导演因同一部电影获导演奖提名<ref name="Kinn-Piazza-2002">{{cite book | last1 = Kinn | first1 = Gail | last2 = Piazza | first2 = Jim | title = The Academy Awards: The Complete Unofficial History | year = 2002 | isbn = 978-1-5791-2396-3 | location = New York, New York, United States | publisher = Workman Publishing Company}}</ref>{{rp|215}}。比蒂还是首位因单部电影获表演、导演、制片和编剧奖提名的电影人。此前[[奧森·威爾斯|奧森·威爾斯]]曾因《[[公民凯恩|公民凯恩]]》获表演、导演和编剧奖提名，但根据当时的评奖规则是是制片商而非制片人获最佳影片奖提名。<ref name="Wiley-Bona-1996" />{{rp|1129}}[[強·沃特|強·沃特]]与[[珍·芳達|珍·芳達]]分获[[奥斯卡最佳男主角奖|影帝]]和[[奥斯卡最佳女主角奖|影后]]，《荣归》（''{{lang|en|Coming Home}}''）是史上第四部拿下男、女主角奖提电影<ref name="Osborne-2013" />{{rp|423}}。[[瑪姬·史密芙|瑪姬·史密芙]]因在《加州套房》扮演获奥斯卡奖提名但未胜出的电影人赢得[[奥斯卡最佳女配角奖|最佳女配角奖]]，是唯一扮演奥斯卡“输家”后获奖的演员<ref name="Osborne-2013" />{{rp|423}}。

